{"_id":"16Pco37gNw24T7lK","name":"Study of the Elements","type":"subclass","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-levitate-blue-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The elemental planes harbor raw power that magi find themselves drawn to. It's a form of natural power they draw from to manipulate the battlefield and empower their strikes. The goal of a magus dedicated to this study is to control these elements and bend them to their will. Some dedicate their study to mastering drawing power from a single elemental plane, and others might attempt to bend all four primordial realms to their whim. Whichever path a novice magus would like to take, they can be assured that they have control of the field and the elements are on their side.</p>\n<h2>Study Spells</h2>\n<p>As a Study of the Elements Magus, you gain the Control Flames cantrip. In addition, you gain the study spells in the table below at the magus levels listed. These spells are always prepared and don't count towards your daily preparations.</p>\n<table style=\"width:100%;height:170px\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:17px\">Magus Level</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:17px\">Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:34px\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:34px\">Absorb Elements, Chromatic Orb</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:34px\">5th</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:34px\">Earthen Grasp, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.FSMy6VAjDnXY9vWz]{Gust of Wind}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:17px\">9th</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:17px\">Elemental Weapon, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.j8NtLXOOJ3GAKF8I]{Protection from Energy}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:34px\">13th</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:34px\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.7fFHlBk3UNX8gPKL]{Control Water}, Elemental Bane, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.QvGcdRUSNRKEQJlK]{Stone Shape}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:17.2676%;height:34px\">17th</td>\n<td style=\"width:82.7324%;height:34px\">Control Winds, Maelstrom</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Study Advancement</h2>\n<p>3rd-level: Bonus Cantrip, @Item[vb4r4b6gRPRThlxO]{Elemental Strike}</p>\n<p>7th-level: @Item[Za7lvYLsFYiHlpjP]{Amplified Gifts}</p>\n<p>15th-level: @Item[86zm7FVOs9YfoC7E]{Elemental Attunement}, @Item[GuRtemWnegL6yzTT]{Planar Traveller}</p>\n<p>20th-level: @Item[hFDMjtVQFpWuk21Q]{Elemental Will}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"THC","identifier":"study-of-the-elements","classIdentifier":"magus","advancement":[],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":"int"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9q0EBbNcXQL6DYVT":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"znzFjC9qoYciasdh","name":"Study of the Sentient Weapon","type":"subclass","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-flanged-lightning.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Magi who follow this study draw their magic from the weapons they wield, enforcing their strikes. They form bonds with the weapons they utilize, and a weapon in turn becomes a valuable tool and ally. As the magus grows in power, so too do the weapons they chose take take with them. A spirit molded by what they choose to hold, the Magus strides forth with trust that their weapons will grant them power.</p>\n<h2>Study Spells</h2>\n<p>As a Study of the Sentient Weapon Magus, you gain the Sword Burst cantrip. Additionally, you gain the study spells in the table below at the magus levels listed. These spells are always prepared and don't count towards your daily preparations.</p>\n<table style=\"width:100%;height:170px\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:17px\">Magus Level</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:17px\">Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:34px\">3rd</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:34px\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.7buEm5KhI5lP8m1z]{Guiding Bolt}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.z1mx84ONwkXKUZd7]{Shield}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:34px\">5th</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:34px\">Cloud of Daggers, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.JbxsYXxSOTZbf9I0]{Spiritual Weapon}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:34px\">9th</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:34px\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Szvk5FEVQW3uhJi5]{Haste}, Tiny Servant</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:34px\">13th</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:34px\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.da0a1t2FqaTjRZGT]{Freedom of Movement}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.1ADstb0Xec6HHRcU]{Resilient Sphere}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:16.8801%;height:17px\">17th</td>\n<td style=\"width:83.1199%;height:17px\">@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.ATo0Eb63TDtnu6iA]{Animate Objects}, Steel Wind Strike</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Study Advancement</h2>\n<p>3rd-level: @Item[hoszt5116tt7wdMh]{Bonus Cantrip}, @Item[g6uYOL5MdgYN1IjH]{Weapon Bond}, @Item[RzZDiBu3QyrV7itl]{Martial Will}</p>\n<p>7th-level: @Item[aBYR2YWckpPNFFa7]{Bonded Awakening}</p>\n<p>15th-level: @Item[sA1ijxTe4QoWJyDO]{Weapon Barrage}</p>\n<p>20th-Level: @Item[bORvt38DHllNq1Tq]{Perfect Bond}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"THC","identifier":"steelbond-study","classIdentifier":"magus","advancement":[{"_id":"r9epwr5hf4kwrkpg","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":[],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"gjjt0fov4btzulqf","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":[],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":7,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"ao77qwciicsn2ify","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":[],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":15,"title":"Features","icon":""},{"_id":"27fimacjxzcyjav9","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":[],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":20,"title":"Features","icon":""}],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":"int"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"9q0EBbNcXQL6DYVT":3},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"bw-dnd5e","system":"dnd5e","coreVersion":"9.269","systemVersion":"1.6.1"}}}
